```css
.swatch {
  color: white;
  width: 100px;
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  text-align: center;

  &:nth-child(1) {
    background-color: var(--bg);
  }
  &:nth-child(2) {
    background-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg), black 30%);
  }
  &:nth-child(3) {
    background-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg), white 30%);
  }
}
```

